STATE of New Jersey, Plaintiff,
v.
Coby T. RICHARDSON, a/k/a Colby Richardson, Colby Timothy Richardson, Defendant. State of New Jersey, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
Jeffery Richardson, a/k/a Jeffery Osborne Richardson, Jeffrey Richardson, Jeffery O. Richardson, Jeffrey Richrardson, Defendant-Petitioner. C-419 September Term 2017
079661 Supreme Court of New Jersey. December 8, 2017

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-4021/4026-14 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
